::Battera/Dachande::

    Battera stopped flying and landed on the ground, =
then she transformed to robot mode. Dachande stopped and did the same, his =
mask slip away from his real face and they hugged and kissed.
    "I shall =
try not to be long," Dachande said.
    "Just don't get yourself killed," B=
attera said. But in the back of her mind she was thinking It wouldn't be go=
od for Voivode Vukodlak's plans for you. They parted ways, both going back =
to Beast mode, Battera flying away, and Dachande running at full speed towa=
rds the Neutral base.
